    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >测试版包含内容：</h2>关卡1-1到1-6、2-1到2-6、3-1，同时包括两个量子翘曲和两个光速逃亡关卡以及一个怪异空间关卡，一共13个主线关卡和5个支线关卡。所有的装备、技能解锁都与关卡进度同步。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246270/extras/ab053e77e5c444997858fc09e4bf2ec5.webp?t=1729403284\" width=700 height=4 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >完整游戏介绍：</h2>《孤行异星》是一款由一个人开发制作完成的独立游戏。<br><br>它的故事发生在距离地球22光年的格利泽667Ce上，那时的地球文明已经陷入重重危机。你将可以单人扮演孤行者杜昊或者佐伊中的一个角色，或者和你的朋友一起在一台设备上同时扮演两位孤行者，操控他们不同特点的战车，在这颗神秘的星球上，寻找到可能拯救地球文明的一丝希望。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246270/extras/ab053e77e5c444997858fc09e4bf2ec5.webp?t=1729403284\" width=700 height=4 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246270/extras/87e428b82bae0926b8c1c53a803fdc40.poster.avif?t=1729403284\" width=640 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246270/extras/87e428b82bae0926b8c1c53a803fdc40.webm?t=1729403284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246270/extras/87e428b82bae0926b8c1c53a803fdc40.mp4?t=1729403284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >本地双人协同，双摇杆控制战斗</h2></li></ul>可以双人同屏，同时控制两个战车，消灭关卡中的全部敌人，并保卫基地。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246270/extras/ab053e77e5c444997858fc09e4bf2ec5.webp?t=1729403284\" width=700 height=4 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246270/extras/28573e39f7cf73436a6325dd74052a2d.poster.avif?t=1729403284\" width=640 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246270/extras/28573e39f7cf73436a6325dd74052a2d.webm?t=1729403284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246270/extras/28573e39f7cf73436a6325dd74052a2d.mp4?t=1729403284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >动态等级，时刻警觉</h2></li></ul>可以通过获取关卡补给，提升速度和炮塔等级，但遭遇攻击时，也有可能降级，需要时刻注意保持战车的等级。<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多种炮弹，组合攻击</h2></li></ul>通过关卡补给，获取不同的炮弹，或者燃烧敌人，或者冰冻敌人，或者呼叫轰炸支援，你甚至可以发射核弹！<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >共同控制，合二为一</h2></li></ul>在有两名玩家的状态下，可以控制同一台坦克，一人驾驶，一人攻击。<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >投掷炮塔，防御敌人</h2></li></ul>可以自由投掷炮塔或障碍物，阻止敌人靠近基地。<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >银河祝福</h2></li></ul>哇哦，用银河祝福恢复生命，但一定注意，如果选错了祝福对象，还会召唤陨石袭击。<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >量子状态，补给另一名玩家</h2></li></ul>在有两名玩家的状态下，如果一名玩家被摧毁，可以进入量子状态，消耗元素补给另一名玩家。<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >丰富的敌人</h2></li></ul>游戏拥有超过1000种不同的敌人，你还会发现一些神秘的强大敌人。<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多元的装备</h2></li></ul>可以利用零件和粒子能力碎片组装或合成丰富的装备。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246270/extras/ab053e77e5c444997858fc09e4bf2ec5.webp?t=1729403284\" width=700 height=4 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246270/extras/b8615cd3b6f9e6491a73fd539a6dcb9c.poster.avif?t=1729403284\" width=640 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246270/extras/b8615cd3b6f9e6491a73fd539a6dcb9c.webm?t=1729403284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246270/extras/b8615cd3b6f9e6491a73fd539a6dcb9c.mp4?t=1729403284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >核聚变，自由聚变元素</h2></li></ul>可以通过核聚变聚变任意元素，用元素合成零件或粒子能量碎片。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246270/extras/ab053e77e5c444997858fc09e4bf2ec5.webp?t=1729403284\" width=700 height=4 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246270/extras/f42fa169ef74dac82f8881df31539c13.poster.avif?t=1729403284\" width=640 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246270/extras/f42fa169ef74dac82f8881df31539c13.webm?t=1729403284\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3246270/extras/f42fa169ef74dac82f8881df31539c13.mp4?t=1729403284\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >单人模式</h2></li></ul>如果你只想要一个人体验游戏，可以体验到100%的剧情和100%的关卡。<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >银河系历史学</h2></li></ul>跟着杜昊和佐伊一起，抽丝剥茧，解密人类文明的未来和银河系的历史。",
